parameters:
\n< Serena >We've come quite deep... Something feels dim
and chilly around this area.
\n<  >Who is it!?
\n< Serena >Hm?

\n< Serena >...Don't be on guard. It's just a coincidence
that we came here. I heard that valuable
herbs grow around this area.
\n< Serena >I have no business with you.
\n<  >Ah... So.
\n< Serena >What are you doing here?
\n<  >Do you know anything about this place?
\n< Serena >I don't know. It's my first time here.

\n<  >Oh, happiness, huh? That's nice. It's
better not to know.
\n< Serena >Well, I can't quite grasp the situation...

\n<  >It doesn't matter, right? Well then, I'll
take my leave.

\n< Serena >Ah... Hm? That flower you're holding in your
right hand...
\n<  >Huh?

\n< Serena >Translucent blue petals, scattering as they turn
into light and pollen.

\n< Serena >Isn't that the Forget-Me-Not flower...? I
came here to find it.
\n<  >...Hah... Is this what you want?

\n< Serena >It's necessary. There's no other choice
around here...

\n<  >No, there isn't. This is all. I've taken
care of everything.
\n< Serena >...Then I'll buy that flower for 10G.

\n<  >Oh, you're going to pay money? Is it really
that necessary?

\n< Serena >Honestly, it's not something I need or have any
interest in myself. But it's part of the
request to procure it.
\n<  >Are you in the same line of work?

\n< Serena >Are you dissatisfied with the amount of
money?

\n<  >Hmmm? Well... if it's ten times that amount,
I might consider giving it to you.
\n< Serena >Alright. I'll take it out.
\n<  >Hah? You're kidding, right? 100G? 100G?!

\n<  >There's no way you can get such a large sum of
money for a request to procure this kind
of grass!

\n< Serena >That's true. However, it's not a matter of
money.
\n< Serena >Please. I want you to sell it for 100G.

\n<  >...Hah. How ridiculous... I was just teasing a
kid, that's all.

\n<  >There's no way someone like you, with a small
cock, would have that kind of money.
\n<  >It's fine, I'll give it to you for free.
\n< Serena >Huh?... I-Is it okay?

\n<  >It's like a weed. Around here, it grows
abundantly if you leave it alone.
\n<  >...Seriously, one after another, these people...

\n< Serena >I don't really understand, but... Thank
you. I'll express my gratitude. With
this, I can fulfill the request.
\n<  >Hah, that's good to hear.

\n<  >Well then, take care and make sure to safely
return home.
\n< Serena >Ah, let's do that. You take care too.
\n<  >...What the hell are you doing...

\n<  >Ahh, everything is just getting so damn
annoying.
\n<  >Are you giving up, adventurer...

\n<  >...If only that were possible, I wouldn't
have to go through all this trouble...
